    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Need RCF Calculations for Your Application?</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 mb-4">Dolphin Centrifuge engineers calculate required g-force for your specific fluid, particle size, and separation target - then recommend the right centrifuge model.</p>
